results: Genovation Computer Input Devices - Founded in 1989, manufactures computer input devices, keypads, and specialized keyboards, based in Irvine, California, known for producing accessory keypads for computers and POS systems.
Genovation Cars - Electric vehicle manufacturer, known for the GXE electric supercar with 800HP, based in Rockville, Maryland, holds world records for fastest street-legal electric car.

Genovation Health - Healthcare technology company, focuses on precision genomics and population health initiatives, provides pharmacogenetic and clinical decision support solutions, based in Reno, Nevada.
Genovation Group - Specializes in power generation project development, operates throughout North America, has 30 years of industry experience.
Genovation Technologies - IT services company, provides managed IT services and enterprise solutions, focuses on cybersecurity protection and business technology transformation.
Genovation Capital - Former venture capital firm, was based in Groton, Massachusetts, focused on investments in communication, media, and internet sectors.
